abstract: >-
  Artificial Wisdom Guardrail Protocol is an open framework for evaluating
  AI-agent outputs and automation decisions not only by capability, speed,
  or task completion, but also by long-term stability, transparency,
  reversibility, human oversight, accountability, misuse resistance,
  ecological continuity, and civilizational resilience.
